<refsection role="introduction">
<title>Introduction</title>
<para>The <tag>p:validate-with-dtd</tag> step validates XML with a DTD.</para>
</refsection>

<refsection role="step-declaration">
<title>Step declaration</title>
<xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../xmlcalabash/src/main/resources/com/xmlcalabash/library.xpl" xpointer="xpath(/*/*[@type='p:validate-with-dtd'])"/>
</refsection>

<refsection role="errors"><title>Errors</title><para>
<error code="C0210">It is a <glossterm>dynamic error</glossterm>
if the <option>assert-valid</option> option on <tag>p:validate-with-dtd</tag>
is <literal>true</literal>
and the input document is not valid.</error>
</para>
</refsection>

